Return the text of the RegExp pattern:

Copy
let str = "Visit Demo2s.com";
let patt1 = /Demo2s/g;
let res = "The text of the RegExp is: " + patt1.source;
console.log(res);
Output:


Description
The source property returns the text of the RegExp pattern.

Browser Compatibility
Chrome.png	Node.png	Firefox.png	Safari.png	Edge.png	Opera.png
source	Yes	Yes	Yes	Yes	Yes	Yes
Syntax
Copy
RegExpObject.source
Return Value
Type	Description
String	The text of the RegExp pattern
